Saturday Nights with Melissa St. John
Date:
Saturdays
Time:
Showtimes at 9:00 PM and 11:00 PM
Description:
Join us every Saturday night as the fabulous Melissa St. John lights up the stage with unforgettable performances and fierce glamour.
T-Dance & Frosé
Date:
Sundays
Time:
Starts at 6:00 PM
Description:
Sip on $7 frosé all day while you dance, mingle, and soak up the sunshine. No better way to close out the weekend than with a little sparkle and a lot of fun!
